ctrum.ieee.org/robotics/drones/in-the-air-with-ziplines-medical-delivery-drones |title=In the Air with Zipline's Medical Delivery Drones |date=April 30, 2019 |work=[[IEEE Spectrum]] |first1=Evan |last1=Ackerman |first2=Michael |last2=Koziol |accessdate=2019-05-19}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"mit\">{{cite news|url=https://www.technologyreview.com/s/608034/blood-from-the-sky-ziplines-ambitious-medical-drone-delivery-in-africa/|title=Zipline's Ambitious Medical Drone Delivery in Africa |last=Rosen|first=Jonathan W.|work=[[MIT Technology Review]] |date=June 8, 2017 |accessdate=2018-08-24|language=en}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=enables>{{cite web |last=Ezell|first=Stephen|date=August 7, 2017 |title=Zipline Enables Real-time Delivery of Essential Medical Supplies in Rwanda|url=https://itif.org/publications/2017/08/07/zipline-enables-real-time-delivery-essential-medical-supplies-rwanda|language=en}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=robotics>{{cite web |url=http://roboticsandautomationnews.com/2019/05/03/ups-foundation-supports-ghanas-vaccine-drone-delivery-network/22162/ |title=UPS Foundation supports Ghana's vaccine drone delivery network |date=May 3, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=disrupter>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/22/zipline-international-2018-disruptor-50.html|title=2018 Disruptor 50: No. 25 Zipline International |date=May 22, 2018 |work=CNBC|accessdate=2018-10-12}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=drive>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedrive.com/tech/21039/zipline-has-successfully-aerially-delivered-7000-units-of-blood-to-rwandan-hospitals|title=Zipline Has Successfully Aerially Delivered 7,000 Units of Blood to Rwandan Hospitals|last=Margaritoff|first=Marco |date=May 24, 2018 |work=The Drive|accessdate=2018-10-14|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=bono>{{cite web|url=https://www.fastcompany.com/90402575/bono-is-really-into-drones-now-but-its-good|title=Bono is really into drones now (but it's good)|last=|first=|date=September 12, 2019|website=FastCompany|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-dat