175 |title=Drones to deliver vaccines, blood and drugs across Ghana |website=[[Reuters]] |accessdate=2019-05-21}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=ShutDown2>{{cite web|url=http://www.simplebotics.com/2016/02/the-rise-and-fall-of-robot-startup-romotive.html|title=Why Romotive shut down |date=February 8, 2016 |website=Simplebotics|language=en-US|accessdate=2018-12-05}}</ref>\n<ref name=ghanaweb>{{cite web|url=https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Ghana-Health-Service-gives-full-details-of-drone-health-service-delivery-system-706432|title=Ghana Health Service gives full details of drone health service delivery system |date=December 5, 2018 |website=www.ghanaweb.com|accessdate=2018-12-21}}</ref>\n<ref name=india>{{cite web|url=https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/medical-devices/govt-of-maharashtra-and-zipline-announce-indias-first-autonomous-instant-drone-delivery-service/71149101|title=Govt of Maharashtra, Zipline and SII announce India's first autonomous instant drone delivery service - ET HealthWorld|last=www.ETHealthworld.com|website=ETHealthworld.com|language=en|accessdate=2019-10-23}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"crunch\">{{cite web|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/romotive#section-locked-marketplace|title=Zipline International|website=[[Crunchbase]]|accessdate=2018-12-05}}</ref>\n<ref name=army>{{Cite web|url=https://www.commercialdroneprofessional.com/zipline-partners-with-the-us-military-to-test-medical-drones/|title=Zipline partners with the US military to test medical drones|last=Trask|first=Matthew|date=2019-10-23|website=Commercial Drone Professional|language=en-US|accessdate=2019-10-23}}</ref>\n<ref name=ShutDown>{{Cite web|url=http://www.simplebotics.com/2016/02/the-rise-and-fall-of-robot-startup-romotive.html|title=Why Romotive shut down |date=February 8, 2016 |website=Simplebotics|language=en-US|accessdate=2018-12-05}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cnbcAPR2018\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/04/02/zipline-new-zip-2-drone-delivers-suppli